<br />
This is why my tells on my trader go in their own separate window.  After AFK for 10 or so hours, I can easily see who sent me tells.  I don't need pop up boxes for  this.  This is a ridiculous waste of time and energy to implement IMO. <img src="images/smilies/rolleyes.gif" border="0" alt=""></font></p>
	
